1423.name: S2 CrMo1
1423.Applications: Typical applications in power generation plant include steam piping, turbines and boilers; the alloy also finds applications in the chemical and petro-chemical industries.
1423.Suitable_For: heat and creep resistant steel, , GS 22CrMo54, G17CrMo5-5, G22CrMo5-4, 13CrMo 4-5, 16CrMo 4-4, G-17CrMo 5-5, 24CrMo5, 25CrMo4, 21 CrMo 3, 25 CrMo 4, 17CrMo55ASTM: A182 grades F11/F12, A199/A200 grade T11, A217 grades WC6/WC11, A234 grades WP11/WP12, A335 grades P11/P12, A387 grades 11/12
